# Cloudflare Pages routing rules.
#
# 1) Proxy API calls to the Fly.io backend.  The web client uses
#    relative paths like fetch('/api/v1/...') so Pages must rewrite
#    them to the API origin.  Status 200 = proxy (not redirect).
/api/*  https://ai-plot-twist.fly.dev/api/:splat  200

# 2) SPA fallback — every non-matching route returns index.html so
#    the Svelte client-side router can render it.
/*  /index.html  200
